1. *Uživaš* li u ovoj predivnoj večeri? (Are you enjoying this wonderful evening?)
2. On *uživa* u svakom zalogaju hrane. (He enjoys every bite of his food.)
3. *Uživali* smo u predivnom pogledu s vrha planine. (We enjoyed the beautiful view from the top of the mountain.)
4. Ne mogu da verujem koliko *uživaš* u tome da me nerviraš. (I can't believe how much you enjoy annoying me.)
5. Ona *uživa* u čitanju knjiga. (She enjoys reading books.)
6. Nadam se da ćeš *uživati* u ovoj izložbi. (I hope you will enjoy this exhibition.)
7. Svi *uživaju* u letnjim danima. (Everyone enjoys summer days.)
8. *Uživaj* u svom odmoru na moru! (Enjoy your vacation by the sea!)
9. Želim da ti kažem da *uživam* u tvojem društvu. (I want to tell you that I enjoy your company.)
10. *Uživaš li* u svojoj novoj kancelariji? (Are you enjoying your new office?)